SpruceMedia,is,a,social,advertising,platform,allowing,users,to,manage,their,advertisments,on,Facebook,SpruceMedia,offers,an,API,that,allows,advertisers,to,provide,scalable,performance,advertising,on,Facebook,to,their,customers,or,within,their,product,The,API,provides,functionality,across,areas,including,advertisers,ads,campaigns,groups,and,specs,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON